claim.claim-text:
1. An information handling system comprising:
plural processing components operable to process information;
an optical drive interfaced with the processing components, the optical drive operable to read information from an optical medium with a laser and to communicate the information to the processing components, the laser managed with a laser diode having a drive current;
an HFM oscillator interfaced with the drive current and operable to apply an HFM signal to the drive current; and
a frequency controller interfaced with the HFM oscillator and operable to frequency modulate the HFM signal in one or more predetermined patterns.
